gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Util

Class StrTokenObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.nls.lvg.Util.StrTokenObject

  • public class StrTokenObject
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates a fundamental string token object for strip function. The strip function become complicated if it combines with punctuations. This class along with StripToken handle such cases.

    History:

    Version:
    V-2013
    Author:
    NLM NLS Development Team
    See Also:
    StripToken
